{
  "texts": [
    "To categorize the free-text responses, we divided them between two independent coders.",
    "Each coder then cross-checked a random sample of the other's work, with near-complete agreement.",
    "Figures B.1 illustrate that AI chatbots have led to the creation of new tasks across all 11 occupations in our study.",
    "Figure B.2 shows that 50% to 95% of these tasks are directly linked to AI use.",
    "Figure B.3 breaks down the composition of AI-related job tasks by occupation and task category."
  ]
}